# ðŸ” Secure File Share â€“ Backend System

This is a secure file-sharing backend system built with **FastAPI**, implementing access control between two types of users â€“ **Ops Users** and **Client Users**.

This project was built as a solution to the Back-End Intern Test, and includes full authentication, file upload/download logic, encrypted URL generation, and access control.

