### ðŸ‘¤ Client User
- âœ… Sign Up (returns encrypted download URL)
- âœ… Email Verification
- âœ… Login
- âœ… Download file (via secure URL)
- âœ… List all uploaded files

---

## ðŸ” Security & Access Control
- âœ… JWT Authentication for both user types
- âœ… Encrypted download URLs (only valid for client users)
- âœ… Role-based restrictions:
  - Only Ops users can upload
  - Only Client users can download
  - Download links are protected from unauthorized access

